              },
              "blocks": {
                "faq_row_1": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How much water can the vest hold?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_1": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>The vest is compatible with most standard 1.5L–2L hydration bladders (sold separately). The dedicated bladder compartment keeps water accessible on the go, and the chest-mounted tube routing lets you drink without breaking stride.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_1"]
                },
                "faq_row_2": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Will it bounce or shift during a run?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_2": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>No. The vest features adjustable chest straps and a snug wrap-around fit that distributes weight evenly. It sits close to your body to minimize movement, even during trail runs or high-cadence sprints.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_2"]
                },
                "faq_row_3": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Does it fit a phone?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_3": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>Yes! The vest includes a dedicated front chest pocket designed to fit most smartphones up to 6.7 inches. The secure zipper closure and soft inner lining protect your screen during movement.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_3"]
                },
                "faq_row_4": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Is it suitable for both men and women?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_4": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>Yes. The vest comes in multiple sizes and features fully adjustable straps to accommodate a wide range of body types. We recommend measuring your chest circumference and checking the size chart before ordering.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_4"]
                },
                "faq_row_5": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Can I use it for hiking and cycling as well?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_5": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>Absolutely. The vest is designed for multi-sport use — trail running, road running, marathons, mountain biking, and day hikes. The lightweight construction (under 200g) means it won't slow you down regardless of activity.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_5"]
                },
                "faq_row_6": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How do I clean the vest and bladder?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_6": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>The vest itself is hand-wash or machine-wash safe (cold, gentle cycle). For the hydration bladder, rinse with warm water and mild soap after each use and air dry. Avoid bleach or high-heat drying for both.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_6"]
                },
                "faq_row_7": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Is there enough storage for a long run or race?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_7": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>Yes. In addition to the bladder compartment, the vest includes multiple pockets: 2 front chest pockets (phone + gels\/snacks), 1 zippered side pocket, and a back main compartment for layers or extra gear. Ideal for half marathons and beyond.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_7"]
                },
                "faq_row_8": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Is the material breathable?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_8": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>The vest is made from lightweight, breathable mesh fabric that promotes airflow against your back and shoulders. It keeps you cooler during long efforts compared to traditional backpack-style hydration packs.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_8"]
                },
                "faq_row_9": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Does the bladder come included?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_9": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>Please check your selected variant — some bundles include a hydration bladder and others are vest-only. The vest is compatible with most major bladder brands (Platypus, CamelBak, Osprey) with a standard tube diameter.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_9"]
                },
                "faq_row_10": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "What is your return policy?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "question_mark",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "faq_text_10": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": { "text": "<p>We offer a 30-day hassle-free return policy. If the fit isn\u2019t right or you\u2019re not satisfied for any reason, contact us and we\u2019ll arrange a full refund or exchange — no questions asked.<\/p>", "width": "100%" }
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": ["faq_text_10"]
                }
              },
