    "product_reviews_section": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.rv{font-family:var(--font-body--family)}.rv__header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;padding-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.1)}.rv__left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem}.rv__stars-big{color:#FFBE00;font-size:1.5rem;letter-spacing:1px}.rv__count{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}.rv__write-btn{padding:9px 18px;border:1.5px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.4);border-radius:6px;font-weight:600;font-size:.875rem;background:transparent;color:var(--color-foreground);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem}.rv__write-btn:hover{border-color:var(--color-foreground)}.rv__grid{columns:4 220px;column-gap:14px}.rv__card{break-inside:avoid;border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.1);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:14px;background:var(--color-background)}.rv__img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4\/3;object-fit:cover;display:block}.rv__body{padding:14px 16px}.rv__name{font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:2px;color:var(--color-foreground)}.rv__date{font-size:.8rem;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.45);margin-bottom:6px}.rv__stars{color:#FFBE00;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:1px}.rv__text{font-size:.875rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.75)}@media(max-width:749px){.rv__grid{columns:2 160px}}<\/style>{%- assign imgs = product.images -%}<div class=\"rv\"><div class=\"rv__header\"><div class=\"rv__left\"><span class=\"rv__stars-big\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/span><span class=\"rv__count\">20 Reviews &#9660;<\/span><\/div><button class=\"rv__write-btn\">Write a review &#x2261;<\/button><\/div><div class=\"rv__grid\"><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 0 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[0] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Megan T.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/15\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Used this on my first marathon and it was a game changer. No bouncing at all, phone pocket is perfect, and I stayed hydrated the whole race.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 1 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[1] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Chris B.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/8\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Incredibly lightweight. I forget it is on my back. Used it for a 25km trail run and it held everything I needed — water, gels, phone, keys.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 2 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[2] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Rachel S.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/27\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">The fit is snug without being tight. I'm a female runner and this vest actually suits my body shape really well — huge plus.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 3 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[3] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">James L.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/20\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Great for cycling too. The chest pockets are easily accessible while on the bike. Build quality is excellent for the price.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Priya N.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/5\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">I do long hikes every weekend. This vest keeps me hydrated and has just enough room for snacks and a light jacket. Absolutely love it.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Tom W.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/19\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Solid vest. My only note is the bladder tube clip could be a bit firmer, but everything else is perfect. Great value overall.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Linda K.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/12\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">I have tried three different hydration vests over the years and this is by far the most comfortable and breathable. The mesh back panel makes a huge difference in hot weather.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Daniel O.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/18\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Wore it for a 50K ultramarathon. Zero chafing, great storage, and the water flow was smooth the whole way. Will buy again.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Sophie M.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/24\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Fast shipping and great packaging. Vest is exactly as described — lightweight, compact, and very well made. Phone fit perfectly in the chest pocket.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Kevin R.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/22\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Bought this for my wife who runs marathons. She says it is the best gift she has ever received. Now I need one for myself!<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
